1.0.name: wordpress/wp-anniversary
1.0.description:
Allow to select city and display widget with WordPress 10th Anniversary.

Translators

  • Polish (pl_PL) - Marcin Pietrzak

If you have created your own language pack, or have an update of an existing one, you can send gettext PO and MO files to me so that I can bundle it into WP Anniversary. You can download the latest POT file from here.
